=Immanuel Kant=
=Literature= 
==Articles==
* [[Karl-Heinz Pohl]]: Chinese Aesthetics and Kant. International Yearbook of Aesthetics 1 (1996): 14-25
* Martin Müller: Aspects of the Chinese Reception of Kant. Journal of Chinese Philosophy Vol. 33, No.1 (2006): 141-157
* Christian H. Wenzel: Beauty of Kant and Confucius. Journal of Chinese Philosophy 33.1 (2006?): 95-107
* Stephan Schmidt: “Der grosse Chinese von Königsberg: Kants Rolle und Funktion im Kontext der Modernisierung konfuzianischen Denkens im 20. Jahrhundert,” Allgemeine Zeitschrift für Philosophie 33, 1 (2008): 5-29.
* [[Joachim Kurtz]]: "Domesticating a Philosophical Fiction: Chinese Translations of Immanuel Kant's 'Things in Themselves'." Concept and Communication 7 (2011), pp. 165–202 [[@http://has.hallym.ac.kr/Upload/ades_study_data/06%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90%EA%B3%BC%EC%86%8C%ED%86%B57%ED%98%B8_Kurtz.pdf|pdf]]